F.R. JESURATNAM V. UNION OF INDIA & ORS [1981] INSC 119; AIR 1981 SC 1595; 1982 (1) SCR 40; 1981 (3) SCC 525; 1981 (3) SCALE 1056 (22 July 1981)

 PATHAK, R.S.
 PATHAK, R.S.
 REDDY, O. CHINNAPPA (J) 
CITATION: 1981 AIR 1595 1982 SCR (1) 40 1981 SCC (3) 525 1981 SCALE (3)1056 
ACT:
 Right to reinstatement to a post which is subsequently abolished due to the death of the project incharge-Even though the vires of the termination order, which was anterior to the closing of the project, is in issue, Supreme Court can adopt "non-liquet" and decide the case based on the subsequent events.
 
